ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a course on policy and also focuses on leadership a bit too. You will learn a lot about the process of legislation and how you can be involved and make a difference.

N941 is a course about health care policy that covers a wide range of topics from the Iron Triangle to Medicare and Medicaid to healthcare reform. Yes, I would recommend it as policy has a large influence on much that we do.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I think differently about policy and have even more of a desire to be involved.
It deepened my knowledge of how nurses can get involved in policy and the importance of it.
